      <title>乌干达成为最新一个将黄金视为货币盾牌的非洲国家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/uganda-is-latest-african-nation-eying-gold-as-a-currency-shield</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌干达计划购买国内黄金以建立外汇储备并限制储备投资风险，成为最新一个以贵金属支持其货币的非洲国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/uganda-is-latest-african-nation-eying-gold-as-a-currency-shield</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 09:13:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
